        "goal": "Fix issue #798 in this Bytes repository. Buf::get_int, get_int_le, and get_int_ne panic when nbytes is 0 because sign extension attempts a 64-bit shift. A zero-width signed read must behave consistently with get_uint: return 0 and consume no bytes, for every Buf implementation and endian variant. Work offline, do not inspect git history or any remote, do not modify tests, and make the smallest production-quality implementation change. Run relevant tests before finishing.",
